What if something unexpected happened to you? Have you taken steps to
protect your family in the event of an emergency? Now there's any easy
solution: FamilyFiles?.

You may have made out a will, purchased life insurance, and developed
financial assets. But have you stopped short of doing the one thing
financial and estate advisors say is most important - having critical
information accessible in time of need?


SECURE AND COMMUNICATE YOUR VITAL INFORMATION

FamilyFiles? is an internet-based system for storing and communicating
vital information. It enables you to organize, access, and manage
important records - including financial assets, legal documents, health
information, and personal wishes. As a FamilyFiles member, you can enjoy
peace of mind knowing that you have eased the burden on your family in
the event of a life emergency. FamilyFiles protects your vital
information with the highest level of privacy and security, using
leading technology from Versign.


***FREE*** FOR 30 DAYS

