days FREE. At the end of the trial period, if you do not cancel your
membership, you will pay a subscription fee of just $59 a year.

As a FamilyFiles member, you can:

* Organize, secure and manage vital family information
* Protect your family by giving them information for life emergencies
* Save loved ones time and money settling estate matters
* Stay informed with periodic newsletters, alerts, and expert advice
* Automatically convey your legacy decisions to those who need to know
* Enjoy unlimited access to your account from any internet connection


